\f1\b0 Early in the morning Joshua and all the Israelites set out from 
\f0\b Shittim
\f1\b0  and went to the Jordan, where they camped before crossing over.\'a0\cf2 \strokec2 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We started this journey in Shittim\'85because the Israelites weren\'92t willing to finish what they started\uc0\u8232 \
