\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 They were stuck for 40 years in a place they didn\'92t want to be because when they were given the opportunity to step into the promise land they didn\'92t do it\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Today for some of you is that opportunity.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 My hope and prayer for you is that you FINISH\'85you don\'92t walk away from God\'92s best for you\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But\'85and this is what trips every one of us up\'85it requires faith\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 It is impossible to please God without faith and we\'92ll see that again today...\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
